TY  - JOUR
TI  - Non-Symmetric Cardinal Value Allocations
AU  - Scafuri, Allen J.
AU  - Yannelis, Nicholas C.
AB  - [It is shown that cardinal value allocations may fail to be symmetric. Specifically, agents with identical preferences and identical endowments can be treated very differently at a cardinal value allocation. This casts further doubt on the interpretation of the weights as "endogenous utility comparisons."]
